  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the engineers-- it was a day when Schindler wasn't in the camp-- in the factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the engineers went to Leipold and told him, listen, there's a sabotager.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were rules.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If somebody is sabotage, he has to be-- it has to be reported to this and this places, and the man has to be transported to the main camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was a death sentence because if, if you are a saboteur and if you are reported, if you are sent, right, you can only goes to-- go to gas chamber or to be shot or hanged or something like this.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, Schindler wasn't there, but we succeeded to postpone sending the reports [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because in the office where the reports had to be written were Jews, were prisoners working.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the other day or in two days, Schindler came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, Stern and-- mostly Stern approached him and said, listen, this and this happened, and this young man is going to be sent back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he understood that he has to act.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went to Leipold, to this commanding officer, and told him, listen, I know what happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am very furious, and I am-- OK, let-- let's-- let's stop.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
